lead_paragraph: Lee Westwood has advised the six rookies in Europe's Ryder Cup team to brace themselves for a difficult atmosphere in the United States but expects the newcomers to draw on their international experience to flourish in Minnesota.

headline.print_headline: Westwood Backs 'Experienced' Ryder Cup Rookies to Come Good
